2 Data

d <- readMat("StopSearchData.mat")

m <- d$m # 83 자극 x 9 단서 
p <- d$p # 30문제 x 2 자극 번호
v <- as.numeric(d$v) # 9개 단서의 validity
x <- as.numeric(d$x) # 9개 단서의 validity on log-odds evidence scale
y <- d$y # 20명 x 30문제 

n <- dim(m)[1] # 자극 83개
nc <- dim(m)[2] # 단서 9개
nq <- dim(p)[1] # 문제 30개
ns <- dim(y)[1] # 참가자 20명

3 MCMC

data <- list("y", "m", "p", "x", "nc", "nq", "ns")

# parameters to be monitored:
parameters <- c('gamma', 'z', 'phi', 'ypred', 's')

# model
model_text <- "
# Search and Stop
model{
  # Data
  for (i in 1:ns){
    for (q in 1:nq){
      y[i,q] ~ dbern(ttb[t[i,q,z[i,q]+1]])
      ypred[i,q] ~ dbern(ttb[t[i,q,z[i,q]+1]])
    }
  }   
  # TTB Decision
  for (i in 1:ns){
    for (q in 1:nq){    
      for (j in 1:nc){
        tmp1[i,q,j] <- (m[p[q,1],j]-m[p[q,2],j])*pow(2,s[i,j]-1)
      }
      tmp2[i,q] <- sum(tmp1[i,q,1:nc])
      tmp3[i,q] <- -1*step(-tmp2[i,q])+step(tmp2[i,q])
      t[i,q,1] <- tmp3[i,q]+2
    }
  }
  # WADD Decision
  for (i in 1:ns){
    for (q in 1:nq){
      for (j in 1:nc){
        tmp4[i,q,j] <- (m[p[q,1],j]-m[p[q,2],j])*x[j]
      }
      # Find if Cue Favors First, Second, or Neither Stimulus
      tmp5[i,q] <- sum(tmp4[i,q,1:nc])
      tmp6[i,q] <- -1*step(-tmp5[i,q])+step(tmp5[i,q])
      t[i,q,2] <- tmp6[i,q]+2
    }
  }
  # Follow Decision With Probability Gamma, or Guess
  ttb[1] <- 1-gamma
  ttb[2] <- 0.5
  ttb[3] <- gamma
  # Cue Search Order From Ranking stmp
  for (i in 1:ns){
    s[i,1:nc] <- rank(stmp[i,1:nc])
    for (j in 1:nc){
      stmp[i,j] ~ dnorm(0,.001)
    }
  }
  # TTB and WADD Rate Per Subject
  for (i in 1:ns){
    phi[i] ~ dbeta(1,1)
    for (q in 1:nq){
      z[i,q] ~ dbern(phi[i])
    }
  }
  # Priors
  gamma ~ dunif(0.5,1)
}
"
samples <- jags(data, parameters.to.save = parameters, 
                model.file = textConnection(model_text), 
                n.chains=1, n.iter=5000, n.burnin=2000, n.thin=1)
